Package fr.inria.verveine.extractor.java.utils

Class StubBinding

java.lang.Object
fr.inria.verveine.extractor.java.utils.StubBinding
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.IBinding, org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.IMethodBinding, org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ITypeBinding
public class StubBinding extends Object implements org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.IBinding, org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ITypeBinding, org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.IMethodBinding
This is an IBinding implementor to serve as key for unresolved entities.

The Famix dictionary needs an IBinding as entity key. But some entities not fully resolved (eg a class inheriting from an unknown superclass) don't have binding even though we have their declaration. So we create this class that will implement a fake IBinding for such cases.

Only used for entities that may contain other entities (ie types and methods)

Author:
Anquetil
